sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin
    participant API as AdminBillingController
    participant Manual as ManualInvoiceService
    participant Issue as InvoiceIssuanceService

    Admin->>API: POST /admin/billing/invoices/manual
    API->>Manual: createDraft
    Manual-->>Admin: draft invoice

    Admin->>API: POST /admin/billing/invoices/{id}
    API->>Manual: updateDraft (draft only)
    Manual-->>Admin: updated draft

    Admin->>API: POST /admin/billing/invoices/{id}/issue
    API->>Manual: issueDraft
    Manual->>Issue: issueDraft
    Issue-->>Admin: issued invoice (immutable)
